  ('real-estate-appraiser-moex-00194', 'real-estate-appraiser', 'real-estate-appraiser-moex-105-5e22d328', 'sub-real-estate-appraiser-03', NULL, 'essay', '某公司正在考慮投資商業不動產，目前有兩個方案可供選擇，方案 A，租賃期限 10
